name: SIMULACRUM ARMAMENT #027 YOIZUKI MURAMASA
description:
One of the simulacrums of the Muramasa gene, created earlier than #017
Possesses 5 sword skills, one of which is Muramasa's hereditary sword technique that has been programmed into her
Her right eye belongs to someone she snatched when she was fighting for Nano Energon in the digital world, that's when she lost his original eye and got the sword technique that belonged to that eye.
